WEBVTT



00:00:10.016 --> 00:00:13.248
Welcome to the Canopy Roads Baptist Church podcast.

00:00:13.376 --> 00:00:17.472
Our mission is to develop fully devoted followers of Christ.

00:00:17.888 --> 00:00:25.408
On today's episode, we are so excited to have Joy Whithouse reading Psalm 146 as part of our Psalms Project journey.

00:00:29.952 --> 00:00:31.936
Psalm 146:

00:00:32.736 --> 00:00:34.240
Praise the Lord.

00:00:34.208 --> 00:00:36.800
Praise the lord, o my soul.

00:00:37.248 --> 00:00:40.064
I will praise the Lord while I live.

00:00:40.160 --> 00:00:42.976
I will sing praises to my God.

00:00:42.784 --> 00:00:44.800
While I have my being.

00:00:45.120 --> 00:00:48.032
Do not trust in princes

00:00:47.968 --> 00:00:52.064
Immortal man in whom there is no salvation

00:00:52.544 --> 00:00:54.528
His spirit departs

00:00:54.336 --> 00:00:56.736
He returns to the earth.

00:00:56.992 --> 00:00:58.816
And that very day

00:00:58.592 --> 00:01:00.448
His thoughts perish.

00:01:00.864 --> 00:01:02.880
How blessed is he

00:01:02.656 --> 00:01:05.280
Whose help is the God of Jacob?

00:01:05.504 --> 00:01:08.416
whose hope is in the Lord his God.

00:01:09.056 --> 00:01:11.200
who made heaven and earth.

00:01:11.328 --> 00:01:12.768
The sea, it barked.

00:01:12.288 --> 00:01:14.336
And all that is in them.

00:01:15.136 --> 00:01:17.216
Who keeps faith forever

00:01:17.408 --> 00:01:20.576
Who executes justice for the oppressed

00:01:21.184 --> 00:01:23.488
Who gives food to the hungry

00:01:23.584 --> 00:01:26.336
The Lord sets the prisoners free.

00:01:27.168 --> 00:01:30.016
The Lord opens the eyes of the blind.

00:01:30.144 --> 00:01:33.920
The Lord raises up those who are bowed down.

00:01:34.368 --> 00:01:37.184
The Lord loves the righteous.

00:01:37.568 --> 00:01:40.032
The Lord protects the strangers.

00:01:39.936 --> 00:01:43.328
He supports the fatherless and the widow.

00:01:43.808 --> 00:01:46.368
But he thwarts the way of the wicked.

00:01:46.528 --> 00:01:48.864
The Lord will reign forever.

00:01:49.216 --> 00:01:54.752
Your God, O Zion, to all generations, praise the Lord.

00:01:56.032 --> 00:01:58.624
Because God's wills step in.

00:01:58.528 --> 00:02:00.480
Where human help stops

00:02:01.664 --> 00:02:05.024
Or as guards will perform strictly

00:02:04.832 --> 00:02:06.592
Through human action

00:02:14.880 --> 00:02:23.040
We hope this message was encouraging to you. If you would like this kind of content delivered directly to you, consider subscribing to our channel.

00:02:23.104 --> 00:02:32.576
If you'd like more information about our church, please visit us on the web at canopyroads.org. And thanks for listening to the Canopy Roads Baptist Church podcast.
